summary: This show Aggretsuko on Netflix is both the oddest but cutest thing in the world, ok?
body:
This show Aggretsuko on Netflix is both the oddest but cutest thing in the world, ok?

Cannot deny I feel Retsuko. Friends see her as cute, kind and reliable. Which is fine, but then there’s that side that completely loses it up to the point where you cannot possibly be the same being anymore lol.
